      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Good race but the Massingham stable have a huge hand in the race with three top chances. BLUE STRATUM (3) hasn't raced for nine months but his last run was a dominant win over this course and distance. Goes close if on song. Stablemate ALMIGHTY JAB (5) also resumes and is a fresh-up winner. Unbeaten course and distance from two tries and looks very hard to beat. The third stable runner is LADY DAMUS (2) who won the Lightning here at her last run before a break. Also goes well course and distance and will give a start but wind up late. SOWILO SIREN (6) is another resuming and looks the biggest threat to that trio. Won three of his last four before a break. Building a great record here and drawn for a good run. MACHINE HEAD (7) is a speedy galloper placed both tries this course and distance and will give a sight.",
